                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td style="width: 30px; padding-left: 10px;"><i class="fa fa-arrows"></i></td>
                            <td>Ant Commodity has an communication intermediary between producer and buyer who ensures accuracy and fast responses</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
